<div class="content" name="DiskStackType" uuid="be5e6729-e6ef-4ee0-b5cd-bc019d7e6ffa"><p>The <b>DiskStackType</b> enumeration defines valid driver
types that a disk driver is implemented as.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef  enum _DiskStackType
 {
   DiskStackScsiPort = 0x00000000,
   DiskStackStorPort = 0x00000001,
   DiskStackFullPort = 0x00000002
 } DiskStackType;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>DiskStackScsiPort:  </b>The driver is a SCSIPort
driver.</p><p><b>DiskStackStorPort:  </b>The driver is a StorPort
driver.</p><p><b>DiskStackFullPort:  </b>The driver is a monolithic
driver and does not conform to any storage driver submodel.</p></div>